  7. “Phah hou7 li2 si2” (3) 
  Be7 khun3-tit soa3 koh siuN7 tioh8 hit jit8 i phah Le7-hoa5, me7 Le7-hoa5 e5 oe7, koh chit8-ku3 chit8-ku3 ki3 khi2--lai5 siuN7: 
  “But8 chit8-e7 thau2-khui3 leh, e7 hou7 li2 khi3--si2, ian7-thau5 ka7 li2 kong2 seng-khu tioh8 m7-thang bak-kiaN-lang5, li2 chiah thiau-i3-kou3 bak-kiaN-lang5, an2-ni kiam2 e7 khoaN3-tit, chit8 seng-khu be7 su na2 kui2, ia7 teh lau5-phiN7, khoaN3-tioh8 chin chheh” ...... “Be7 tit lin2 pe7 si2 ......”. 
  Ka-ki7 siuN7 liau2 chin phaiN2-se3, gin2-na2 tek8-piat ai3 sng2 chui2, tioh8 e7 ki3-tit Siong7-te3 tui3 khi2-thau5 chiu7-si7 hou7 gin2-na2 tiong2-toa7 ti7 chui2 e5 tiong-kan. EN-a2 chiaN5 thai ti7 lau7-bo2 e5 pak-tou2 te2, chiu7-si7 phu5, a2-si7 chim3, chiu7-si7 koa3 ui siu7 pau ti7 thai-i e5 lai7-bin7, thai-i moa2-moa2 u7 iong5-chui2, ia7 eN-a2 chiu7-si7 chim3 ti7 iong5-chui2 e5 lai7-bin7 kau3 kau3-geh8 chiah seN chhut--lai5. Sou2-i2 gin2-na2 toa7 pou7-hun7 tou si7 ai3 se2-ek8, ai3 bak-chui2, koh lang5 pun2 si7 thou5 chhong3-cho7--e5, sou2-i2 gin2-na2 chin ai3 tiam3 thou5-nih8 pe5, thou5-nih8 so5, li2 na7 hou7 i loh8 khi3 thou5-kha oh8 kiaN5, chiap-tioh8 thou5-khi3, e7 khah nge7-chiaN7, khah khoai3 e7 kiaN5. Gin2-na2 ai3 sng2 thou5 si7 thian-seng3, ai3 sng2 chui2 ia7-si7 thian-seng3. Tek-khak m7 si7 thiau-i3-kou3, ke3-oe7-tek beh khi3-si2 lau7-bo2, chiah beng5-ti kou3-hoan7, phaiN2-sim, ok-i3 hoan7-choe7. Sou2-i2 Siok-cheng siu7-khi3 Le7-hoa5 si7 bo5 i3-su3. 
  “But8 chit8-e7 thau2-khui3 leh” 
  Phah gin2-na2 si7 chhut tui3 thiaN3, ti7 kau3-iok8 siong7 (1) ui7 beh teng3-cheng3 gin2-na2 e5 chho3-gou7, (2) ui7 beh tiam2-chheN2, hou7 i u7 chhim-khek e5 ki3-ek, choe7 e5 kho2-phaN3, (3) phah, chiu7-si7 choe7 e5 kang-chiN5, hou7 lang5 phah i ka-ki7 na2-chun2 kam2-kak tui3 an2-ni, i e5 choe7 na2 chun2 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2 e5 an-sim. Na7-si7 thiaN3 e5 pan2-poe, pan2-poe e5 e7-bin7 u7 thiaN3 e5 bak8-sai2, u7 si5 chin u7 i3-gi7, m7-ku2 na7-si7 phah “thau2-khui3--e5” an2-ni si7 bo5 i3-su3. An2-ni phah gin2-na2 choe3 li2 e5 siau-khi3-tang5, siau-khi3-san2, na7 bo5 phah--lang5, li2 e5 khi3 m7 chiu7 be7 siau, tiaN7 kek-leh e5 khoan2, an2-ni phah si7 siau li2 e5 khi3, bok8-koai3 hou7 li2 phah e5 gin2-na2 m7-goan7--li2. 
  Me7 gin2-na2 si7 “thiau-i3-kou3” che si7 oan-ong2, si7 chiong bo5 iaN2 e5 choe7 lai5 ka-bu5 ti7 be7 hiau2 pian7-hou7 iu3-ji5 e5 teng2-bin7, si7 chin ong2-khut gin2-na2 e5 bu5-sia5 thian-chin. Si7 me7 iaN5 si7-siau3, bo5 kian3-lip8 li2 e5 tek-heng7, ia7 bo5 li7-ek gin2-na2 e5 kau3-iok8. 
  “KhoaN3-tioh8 chin chheh ....... be7 tit lin2 pe7 si2 ...... ”. Gin2-na2 long2 be7 hiau2 li2-kai2. A-bu2 si7 ma-ma, thai3 e7 piN3 lau7-pe7, an2-choaN2 ma-ma e7 chin chheh--i. Put-ti put-kak e7 piN3 “ui3-khu7” kiaN-hiaN5, bo5 chhin, u7 keh-mouh8 e5 kam2-kak, pe7-kiaN2, bo2-kiaN2 m7-thang hou7 se3-kiaN2 seN khi2 ui3-khu7, kiaN-ui3 e5 sim, kiaN2 tui3 pe7-bo2 eng3 u7 e5 sim si7 “keng3-ui3” m7 si7 “kiaN-ui3”. Tui3 chun-keng3 lai5 seN-chhut sun7-hok8 chiah ho2, m7-thang hou7 si7-se3 tui3 kiaN--li2, chiah seN-chhut sun7-hok8, an2-ni m7 ho2. Koh bo5 keng2 ui7, bo5 keng2 chhoe5-a2 giah8 khi2--lai5 loan7-but8, u7 si5 chin sit-pai7, koh khah khok-heng5 chiu7-si7 phah liau2, hou7 lang5 phah e5 gin2-na2 chin thiaN3 teh hau2, tng i teh hau2 e5 si5 chek-si5 kio3 i tiam7-tiam7, lian5 chhng2 tou m7-thang, to7 be7 eng7-tit, na7 chhng2 beh koh phah, chin-chiaN3 heng5-gek8, pi2 keng2-chhat heng5-su7 teh heng5 hoan7-lang5 koh khah chan5-jim2. 
  Lang5 hou7 lang5 phah tak8 e5 tou e7 thiaN3, thiaN3 chiu7 e7 hau2, hau2 chiaN3-chiaN3 si7 thau2-khui3, hou7 lang5 phah e5 si5 sin5-keng chin kin2-tiuN, chin thong3-khou2, sim-chong7 chin chheng2, huih sit-loh8 peng5-heng5, hut-jian5 iu7 kio3 i chek-si5 tioh8 tiam7, m7-thang chhng2, khau3 hou-khip chu7-jian5 e7 khah kin2, hi3-the2, khi3-kng2 chu7-jian5 e7 sit-loh8 siong5-thai3, u7 si5 hou-khip e7 be7 sun7, kio3 i chek-si5 tioh8 tiam7, be7 su ki-khi3, sui-jian5 tian7-liu5 chhiat tng7, ma7 iau2 e7 ke tng2 chit8-e7-a2 chiah tiam7. Sou2-i2 gin2-na2 nge7 tong3 tiam7 i e5 kam2-cheng5, hiat-liu5, khi3-the2 e5 eng-kai-jian5 iau2 e7 u7 e5 oah8-tang7, u7 si5 gin2-na2 e7 ti3-kau3 hoat sio, thau5-khak gong5, m7-na7 kau3-iong2-siong7 bo5 tat8 bok8-tek, ji5-chhiaN2 tui3 gin2-na2 sin-the2 seng-li2-siong7 ia7-si7 chin ok eng2-hiong2. Sou2-i2 thang kong2 phah gin2-na2 m7 si7 te7-it ho2 e5 kau3-siu7 hoat si7 sit8. 
  Eng7 phah lai5 ka3 gin2-na2, m7 tat8-tioh8 eng7 o-lo2 lai5 leng2-to7 iau2 khah ho2, chin chhut-mia5 e5 oe7 an2-ni kong2, “Li2 eng7 chit8-ka-lun5 e5 tok8-ioh8 lai5 beh liah8 hou-sin5, m7 tat8-tioh8 eng7 chit8-tiam2-a bit8, liah8 iau2 khah che7.” Li2 eng7 piN3-bin7 jiong2, hang2-hoah, phah lai5 ka3 gin2-na2, na7 oaN7 choe3 eng7 chhio3-iong5, chhin-chhiat e5 chi2-si7 li2 siuN7 an2-choaN2? PeN5-peN5 e5 ke2-oaN7 lai5 kong2, kiam2-chhai2 chit8-bin7 e7 chiaN5 choe3 chek-oan3, gui7-sian7, ke2-choe3 e5 hang5-hok8, chit-peng5 e7 chiaN5-choe3 chhin-bit8-kam2, tui3 sim-te2 e5 hoaN-hi2 hang5-hok8 ia7 bo5 tek-khak, chong2-si7 u7 lang5 si7 liah8 choe3 bo5 kiu3-kiu3 jiong2, bo5 phah, si7 sit-loh8 si7-toa7-lang5 e5 koan5-ui, che si7 chin toa7 e5 chho3-gou7. 
  Siok-cheng ka-ki7 siuN7 kau3 chia chin kian3-siau3, chiu7 koat-sim ai3 ke2-oaN7 i ka3 gin2-na2 e5 hong-hoat. Sou2-i2 i chiu7 khi2-lai5 kui7-loh8 ki5-to2, kiu5 Chu2 siuN2-su3 i u7 ti3-hui7 thang ka3-si7 i e5 se3-kiaN2. Tui3 hit si5 khi2 i siong5-siong5 chu3-i3 gian2-kiu3 ji5-tong5 sim-li2, kap sek-eng3 ji5-tong5 sim-li2 e5 kau3-siu7-hoat. 
  TaN lan2 na7 beh gian2-kiu3 ji5-tong5 sim-li2 kap hit e5 sek-eng3 ji5-tong5 sim-li2 e5 kau3-siu7 hoat u7 che7-che7 hoat-tou7. 
  1. Chu3-i3 lan2 sin-piN e5 se3-kiaN2, tak8-jit8 e5 seng-oah8, put-lun7 i e5 kong2 oe7, ku2-tong7 it-chhe3. 
