  8. Hu3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7 (1) 
  Tui3 kap Iu3-ti7-hng5 e5 po2-bo2 tam5-lun7 au7, Siok-cheng chiu7 chai i tui3 ka3 gin2-na2 e5 hong-hoat iau2 chin bo5 kau3-giah8. Sou2-i2 hit-ni5 joah8-thiN e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7, i chiu7 poah-kang khi3 ka-jip8, ti7 hit tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 kang2-te5 kio3-choe3 “Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8 e5 chin the5” si7 L. J. S. bok8-su kong2--e5, i chiu7 chin ti3-i3 ka7 i thiaN. ThiaN liau2 hui-siong5 e5 kam2-tong7, chiu7 koh khah beng5-pek8 “Chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8?” TaN chiong bok8-su sou2 kong2 e5 kai3-siau7 ti7 chia. 
  Sim2-mih8 kio3-choe3 Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8? Lan2 tioh8 tai7-seng liau2-kai2 “Seng3-keng” si7 sim2-mih8? Seng3-keng kan2-tit lai5 kong2 chiu7-si7 “Siong7-te3 e5 oe7.” 
  TaN Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 u7 tui3 3 hong-bin7 lai5 piau2-beng5. 
  1. Tui3 sian-ti lai5 soan-iong5. 
