  Lan2 na7 khoaN3 Ku7-iok sian-ti e5 chheh, lan2 siong5-siong5 beh hoat-hian7 chhin-chhiuN7 e7-bin7 e5 oe7. 
  “Goa2 Ia5-ho5-hoa kong2” (I2-sai3-a 1:18).“Ia5-ho5-hoa chhin-chhui3 kong2.” (I2-sai3-a 1:20).“Ia5-ho5-hoa hoan-hu3 Mou5-se kong2.” (Li7-bi7-ki3 6:1, 8).“Long2 si7 chiau3 Ia5-ho5-hoa hoan-hu3 Mou5-se e5.” (Li7-bi7-ki3 8:9).“Chhit-goeh8 ji7-chap8-it jit8, Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 oe7 thok sian-ti Hap-kai kong2.” (Hap-kai 2:1). 
