  Tui3 teng2-bin7 e5 oe7 lan2 chiu7 chai Seng3-keng si7 Siong7-te3 bek8-si7 lai5 sia2 e5 keng. Lang5 m7-thang sui5-pian7 san-tu5 a2-si7 ke-thiN. 
  3. Tui3 Ia5-sou chhin-chhui3 e5 sou2 kong2, kap I e5 sou2 kiaN5 lai5 hian2-beng5. 
  Hui-lek8 ka7 I kong2 “Chu2 ah, eng7 Pe7 hou7 goan2 khoaN3, chiu7 kau3-giah8. Ia5-sou ka7 i kong2, Hui-lek8 Goa2 kap lin2 tiam3 chiah ku2, li2 iau2 m7-bat Goa2 mah? I2-keng khoaN3-kiN3 Goa2 e5, chiu7-si7 khoaN3-kiN3 Pe7.” (Iok-han7 14:8, 9). 
  Ia5-sou kio3 kong2, “Sin3 Goa2 e5 lang5 m7 si7 sin3 Goa2, chiu7-si7 sin3 chhe Goa2 e5. KhoaN3-kiN3 Goa2 e5, chiu7-si7 khoaN3-kiN3 chhe Goa2 e5....... Lang5 na7 thiaN Goa2 e5 oe7 ia7 m7 siu2, Goa2 bo5 sim2-phoaN3 i; in-ui7 Goa2 lai5, m7 si7 beh sim2-phoaN3 se3-kan, si7 beh kiu3 se3-kan. Khi3-sak Goa2, ia7 m7 chiap-lap8 Goa2 e5 oe7 e5 lang5, chiu7 u7 sim2-phoaN3 i e5, chiu7-si7 Goa2 sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2, beh ti7 boat8-jit8 sim2-phoaN3 i. In-ui7 Goa2 sou2 kong2 m7 si7 chhut ti7 ka-ki7, chiu7-si7 chhe Goa2 e5 Pe7, I u7 beng7-leng7 Goa2, tioh8 thoan5 sim2-mih8, kong2 sim2-mih8. Goa2 chai I e5 beng7-leng7 si7 eng2-oah8, sou2-i2 Goa2 sou2 kong2 e5, si7 chiau3 Pe7 sou2 thoan5 hou7 Goa2 e5, lai5 kong2 i.” (Iok-han7 12:44－50). 
  An2-ni, Siong7-te3 chiong Ia5-sou Ki-tok kang3-se3 ti7 se3-kan, chiu7-si7 I pun2-sin ka-ki7 tian2-khui lek8-su2-tek e5 khe2-si7 ti7 se3-kan. Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8 chiu7-si7 kin-ku3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 lai5 ka3-si7; sou2-i2 si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 chhut-hoat, eng7 Siong7-te3 seng3-kiat e5 thiaN3 lai5 leng2-to7 pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2 (hak8-seng) kau3 ti7 Siong7-te3, chiu7-si7 chhoa7 hak8-seng kau3 ti7 Chu2, thang siu7 Chu2 e5 po2-huih se2-chheng, teng5-thau5-siN, chheng-gi7, chiaN5-seng3, ng3 oan5-choan5 chhin-chhiuN7 ThiN-pe7 e5 oan5-choan5 e5 bok8-phiau lai5 chian5-chin3. Chit-khoan2 e5 kau3-iok8 kio3-choe3 “Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8.” 
  “Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8 e5 chin the5”, oaN7 chit8-ku3 oe7 lai5 kong2, chiu7-si7 “Ki-tok-kau3 e5 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8?” Koh oaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, chiu7-si7 “Chu2-jit8-oh8 (kau3-hoe7 hak8-hau7) e5 kau3-iok8-tek kin-pun2 goan5-li2 tau3-ti2 ti7 to2-ui7?” Kiam2-chhai2 u7 chin che7 thang kong2, na7-si7 sio2-ti7 chit si5 si7 beh kiok8-han7 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-iok8 lai5 kong2 na7-tiaN7. 
  (1) Chiu7-si7 kong2 lan2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 eng-kai kin-ku3 sim2-mih8 lai5 ka3? (2) Ia7 eng-kai tioh8 an2-choaN2-iuN7 lai5 ka3? 
  TaN lan2 eng-kai tioh8 kin-ku3 Seng3-keng, Seng3-keng si7 sim2-mih8? Si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 Seng3-keng e5 poe3-au7 u7 sim2-mih8? U7 Siong7-te3 pun2-sin. Sou2-i2 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-iok8 e5 kin-ku3 si7 Siong7-te3, tui3 Siong7-te3 chhut-hoat, eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 lai5 leng2-to7, poe5-iok8 hak8-seng, koh kau3-boe2 si7 chhoa7 hak8-seng kau3 Siong7-te3, an2-ni chiu7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 sou2 kong2 “Tui3 sin3 kau3 ti7 sin3 e5 kang-chok.”
