  9. Hu3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7 (2) 
  1. Seng3-keng kau3-iok8-hak8 e5 bok8-tek? 
  OaN7-oe7 lai5 kong2, siat Chu2-jit8-oh8 ka3 hak8-seng e5 bok8-tek chai7 ti7 to2-ui7? 
